summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 77W, Page 181 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Blocks 103 and 104 of Sherman's HighLand Park Addition, (unrecorded) from Multiple Residence Low Density RM 800 to Single Family Residence High Density RS 5000 zone.
